1
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:37,260
=The Glory=

2
00:01:37,300 --> 00:01:41,140
=Episode 21=

3
00:01:41,660 --> 00:01:45,100
(Deng Mansion)

4
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:48,590
The messenger's identity is unknown.

5
00:01:48,590 --> 00:01:50,480
Make sure to watch
over Mr. Deng's every move.

6
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,600
Alright.

7
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,510
Be careful.

8
00:02:06,870 --> 00:02:08,000
Watch over both the gates.

9
00:02:08,150 --> 00:02:09,960
Keep an eye on anyone suspicious.

10
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:10,920
Yes.

11
00:02:18,620 --> 00:02:20,190
(A Virtuous Legacy)
Come on, higher.

12
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:21,310
Come on.

13
00:02:21,310 --> 00:02:22,990
Alright, that's enough.

14
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:24,680
Good.

15
00:02:25,750 --> 00:02:27,630
Master, we have a guest.

16
00:02:28,030 --> 00:02:30,590
Who is it?
Why haven't you invited them in?

17
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,150
Alright, alright.

18
00:02:32,150 --> 00:02:32,990
Grandfather.

19
00:02:34,590 --> 00:02:36,120
It's Ms. Zhuang Hanyan.

20
00:02:36,870 --> 00:02:37,960
She's come uninvited.

21
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,360
She must be up to no good.

22
00:02:39,590 --> 00:02:40,960
I've seen her before.

23
00:02:41,370 --> 00:02:43,470
She's a clever and proper young lady.

24
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,960
Grandfather, haven't you heard?

25
00:02:46,090 --> 00:02:48,160
She's full of schemes
and is good at currying favor.

26
00:02:48,190 --> 00:02:49,500
At this year's Lantern Festival,

27
00:02:49,590 --> 00:02:52,240
Noble Consort Miao
even gifted her a jade bangle.

28
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:56,240
She's even associated
with Noble Consort Miao?

29
00:03:02,470 --> 00:03:04,430
Greetings, Mr. Deng, Young Master Zaiye.

30
00:03:04,870 --> 00:03:07,120
We didn't know you'd come.

31
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,510
Sorry for not welcoming you sooner.

32
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:09,840
Zhuang Hanyan,

33
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:12,910
we didn't send you an invitation, right?

34
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:15,880
I've long heard that Mrs. Deng is known
for her virtue and chastity,

35
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:18,430
and now she's been praised
by the Emperor.

36
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:20,700
(A Virtuous Legacy)
So, I wanted to pay my respects

37
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:21,850
and came uninvited.

38
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,910
Mr. Deng, please forgive me.

39
00:03:25,310 --> 00:03:26,840
Mrs. Fu, how considerate of you.

40
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,470
Your admiration for virtue and chastity

41
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:30,150
is indeed a comfort to us.

42
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:32,800
Please have a seat and enjoy some tea.

43
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,470
Mrs. Fu, this way, please.

44
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:47,520
Congratulations, Mr. Deng.

45
00:03:47,870 --> 00:03:49,680
- Wenzheng.
- Mr. Deng.

46
00:04:15,660 --> 00:04:16,700
(Quelling the Rebels)

47
00:04:20,070 --> 00:04:22,040
(A Virtuous Legacy)
Very good.

48
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:25,040
This is the Emperor's own handwriting.

49
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,390
What honor for your family.

50
00:04:27,390 --> 00:04:29,630
Mr. Deng, how fortunate you are.

51
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:31,950
Wenzheng,

52
00:04:32,390 --> 00:04:33,680
that's not true.

53
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,950
Who in the court doesn't know

54
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,680
that Mr. Deng cares most

55
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:39,560
about family reputation and integrity?

56
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:42,310
It's only natural for him

57
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:44,390
to receive this honor today.

58
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,200
- Yes.
- Congratulations.

59
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,120
Miss Deng Chan.

60
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:50,630
Miss, this is Mrs. Fu.

61
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:57,800
A woman's virtue

62
00:04:58,870 --> 00:05:00,270
lies most in her chastity.

63
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:04,630
Mr. Zheng, you're quite fortunate.

64
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:08,210
Once your son marries
Mr. Deng's granddaughter,

65
00:05:08,210 --> 00:05:09,680
as she will inherit her mother's will,

66
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,520
your family will also

67
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:12,680
enjoy this great honor

68
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,600
soon enough.

69
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:18,120
Wenzheng, stop this nonsense.

70
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:20,630
Are you cursing my son?

71
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,600
Of course not. Come on.

72
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,680
Of course, I dare not.

73
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:26,040
Greetings, My Lords.

74
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:28,560
Today, you're the star.

75
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:30,070
Please take your seat.

76
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,070
Take your seat.

77
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:36,240
- Yes.
- Everyone.

78
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,190
Come on.

79
00:05:37,190 --> 00:05:38,040
Have a look.

80
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,440
Take a look.

81
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:41,270
Congratulations.

82
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,360
- A virtuous legacy.
- Sorry to keep you waiting.

83
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,680
Mrs. Deng is here.

84
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,750
Hurry. Please sit inside.

85
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,140
Everyone, please take a seat.

86
00:05:50,630 --> 00:05:52,070
Alright, sit down.

87
00:05:53,950 --> 00:05:56,160
You've been a widow for years,
living in solitude.

88
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,630
It must have been difficult for you.

89
00:05:58,750 --> 00:05:59,950
In my opinion,

90
00:05:59,950 --> 00:06:02,270
there is no easy life for any woman.

91
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,510
Being a widow is painful,

92
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:07,000
but caring for the husband and kids
is also hard.

93
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:10,000
Each has its own struggles.

94
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,360
At least Mrs. Deng has received

95
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:13,310
a plaque from the Emperor.

96
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,750
But what about us?

97
00:06:17,390 --> 00:06:18,680
What's happening?

98
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,310
Today is a day of celebration.

99
00:06:20,510 --> 00:06:21,750
Let's all raise a cup

100
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:22,890
to Mrs. Deng.

101
00:06:22,910 --> 00:06:25,390
- Here. To Mrs. Deng.
- Yes. To Mrs. Deng.

102
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:26,960
To Mrs. Deng.

103
00:06:30,970 --> 00:06:32,150
- Come on.
- Cheers.

104
00:06:32,330 --> 00:06:33,210
Please.

105
00:06:33,710 --> 00:06:34,620
One more drink.

106
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:37,730
Alright, alright.

107
00:06:37,730 --> 00:06:38,610
Let's drink.

108
00:06:38,610 --> 00:06:39,450
One more drink.

109
00:06:39,450 --> 00:06:40,290
Fill it up.

110
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:42,060
Sure.

111
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:44,490
One more drink to you.

112
00:06:44,490 --> 00:06:45,760
A virtuous legacy.

113
00:06:48,090 --> 00:06:49,230
How talented.

114
00:06:50,810 --> 00:06:51,690
Good.

115
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:15,640
Qing,

116
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,850
did you see Zhuang Hanyan?

117
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:18,570
Young Master,

118
00:07:18,570 --> 00:07:20,070
Mrs. Fu said she was going to change.

119
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:21,240
I feared she might get lost,

120
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,260
so I followed her out,

121
00:07:22,310 --> 00:07:23,310
but I couldn't find her.

122
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,600
My son,

123
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:52,830
your mother has been
bedridden for years,

124
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:56,160
praying for your well-being in heaven,

125
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,160
so that you may protect our family.

126
00:07:59,040 --> 00:07:59,950
Now,

127
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:02,000
she's finally had her wish fulfilled.

128
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:04,360
For 16 years,

129
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:06,480
Zhang has devoted herself to chastity

130
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:09,180
(Spirit Tablet of Deng Xiangzhao)
and has been filial and dutiful.

131
00:08:09,390 --> 00:08:10,390
Today,

132
00:08:10,970 --> 00:08:12,630
she's been honored
with a chastity plaque

133
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:14,430
by the Emperor.

134
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:18,160
(Outstanding Descendants)
This is an honor for our family

135
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:20,510
and for you.

136
00:08:22,430 --> 00:08:23,270
Grandfather.

137
00:08:23,630 --> 00:08:25,240
Zaiye, come here.

138
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,190
Come here to talk to your father.

139
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:28,030
Grandfather,

140
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:30,120
I just saw Zhuang Hanyan

141
00:08:30,310 --> 00:08:31,920
sneak out from the banquet.

142
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:32,870
I followed her,

143
00:08:33,270 --> 00:08:34,790
but somehow, she vanished.

144
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:37,360
Did you hear anything unusual?

145
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,200
How is it?

146
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:41,510
I didn't see anything wrong.

147
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,080
The banquet is almost over.

148
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,790
Could it be that your info was wrong?

149
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,440
Who are you?

150
00:08:58,030 --> 00:09:00,000
That should be my question.

151
00:09:00,630 --> 00:09:02,750
Sir, who are you?

152
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,240
Why did you sneak

153
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:06,510
into the Dengs' inner chambers so late?

154
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,870
I am Cheng Lei, a student
of the Directorate of Education.

155
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:12,120
I came tonight

156
00:09:13,390 --> 00:09:15,200
to deliver something to Mr. Deng.

157
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,320
So, it was you.

158
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,270
What do you mean?

159
00:09:22,190 --> 00:09:24,950
It is improper for an outsider
to trespass into the inner chambers.

160
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:27,080
Mr. Deng ordered me
to wait for you here.

161
00:09:27,390 --> 00:09:28,600
Give me it.

162
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,200
This...

163
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,270
This is extremely valuable.

164
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:35,240
I must deliver it to Mr. Deng in person.

165
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,910
Grandfather,
you've always been reserved,

166
00:09:48,630 --> 00:09:49,870
yet you drank so much tonight.

167
00:09:49,870 --> 00:09:50,710
Let's go.

168
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:51,840
I'm glad.

169
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,200
I'm so glad.

170
00:10:03,510 --> 00:10:04,900
I thought we'd leave empty-handed,

171
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,120
but after a twist of fate,

172
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,480
we still obtained it.

173
00:10:09,780 --> 00:10:11,940
(Legend of Huayue)

174
00:10:24,510 --> 00:10:25,960
Why is it a novel?

175
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,420
Where is the joint memorial?

176
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:29,030
It seems the man from earlier

177
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,240
wasn't the messenger.

178
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,910
Then why did he sneak
into the Deng Mansion

179
00:10:32,910 --> 00:10:34,050
in the middle of the night?

180
00:10:39,150 --> 00:10:42,120
The small regular script is clearly
written by a woman.

181
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:44,440
Look.

182
00:10:44,910 --> 00:10:46,480
This novel has

183
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,750
a lot of red comments.

184
00:10:48,630 --> 00:10:50,910
They're probably from a man.

185
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:53,360
There's a name signed in the comments.

186
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:55,000
Cheng Lei.

187
00:10:56,870 --> 00:10:58,390
Didn't the young master just say

188
00:10:58,390 --> 00:10:59,750
his name was Cheng Lei?

189
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:00,870
Yes.

190
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:02,750
That's it.

191
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:04,700
(By Chan Zhixue)
The author is Chan Zhixue.

192
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:06,000
It must be Deng Chan.

193
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:08,030
Those two...

194
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,950
They left these comments to each other.

195
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:13,600
Let's take a look

196
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,870
to find out how they met

197
00:11:14,870 --> 00:11:16,070
and what their relationship is.

198
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:22,080
At the lantern banquet,

199
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:24,240
I found this book by accident.

200
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:26,740
(Lantern Banquet)

201
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:33,800
Chan.

202
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,320
Chan.

203
00:11:36,670 --> 00:11:37,510
Coming.

204
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,060
At the lantern banquet,

205
00:11:41,060 --> 00:11:42,670
I found this book by accident.

206
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:46,320
I carefully read it,
but it was not enough.

207
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,030
I boldly added some comments in red

208
00:11:49,030 --> 00:11:50,390
and left it at Linjiang Pavilion.

209
00:11:50,390 --> 00:11:51,390
(Legend of Huayue)

210
00:11:51,390 --> 00:11:52,840
If you happen to collect it

211
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,080
and continue the story,

212
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:56,240
can you still leave it
at Linjiang Pavilion?

213
00:11:56,550 --> 00:11:58,390
I'll visit every day to ask around.

214
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:00,440
Hopefully, I can read the rest.

215
00:12:01,030 --> 00:12:02,360
Ms. Qu is a charming woman.

216
00:12:02,630 --> 00:12:04,840
She's unconventional and brave,

217
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:07,970
(Legend of Huayue by Chan Zhixue)
breaking out of the mundane world.

218
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:10,030
You must be like this too.

219
00:12:10,910 --> 00:12:12,080
I admire you,

220
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:13,670
and my heart longs for you.

221
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:15,870
(Legend of Huayue)
I hope we can meet.

222
00:12:15,940 --> 00:12:17,790
(They ignore the moon)

223
00:12:17,790 --> 00:12:19,270
The world loves appearances,

224
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,750
but I alone cherish the soul.

225
00:12:22,870 --> 00:12:25,030
Mr. Meng and Ms. Qu
are meant to be together.

226
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:29,550
Ms. Zhixue, we know each other
through literature.

227
00:12:30,390 --> 00:12:31,840
Is it also bound by destiny?

228
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:34,000
(Dressed in simple attire,
she went to offer advice.)

229
00:12:34,060 --> 00:12:35,220
Like Mr. Meng,

230
00:12:35,670 --> 00:12:38,360
I've fallen in love with a woman
who is unique in this world.

231
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:41,000
She haunts my dreams,

232
00:12:41,670 --> 00:12:42,840
and I can't sleep at night.

233
00:12:44,550 --> 00:12:45,630
I've fallen for you,

234
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,730
but I wonder what you think of me.

235
00:12:48,830 --> 00:12:51,190
I am Cheng Lei, a student
of the Directorate of Education.

236
00:12:51,190 --> 00:12:53,050
I don't have a prominent family
or much talent,

237
00:12:53,110 --> 00:12:54,640
but I have a sincere heart.

238
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:57,240
I hereby propose to you.

239
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,320
I'll wait for you

240
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:00,920
at Changle Pavilion.

241
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,000
Thanks to your encouragement,

242
00:13:03,750 --> 00:13:05,910
Legend of Huayue can continue its story.

243
00:13:06,270 --> 00:13:09,030
(Legend of Huayue by Chan Zhixue)
Yet it's just a fleeting illusion.

244
00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:11,540
I've been long trapped
in the inner chambers.

245
00:13:11,740 --> 00:13:13,110
To meet someone who understands me

246
00:13:13,150 --> 00:13:16,150
through literature
is already a stroke of luck.

247
00:13:16,910 --> 00:13:19,080
You're a student with high aspirations

248
00:13:19,670 --> 00:13:20,790
of the Emperor,

249
00:13:22,030 --> 00:13:24,030
while I have been engaged.

250
00:13:24,390 --> 00:13:25,560
I'm not the right one for you.

251
00:13:25,750 --> 00:13:27,150
Today, this is my farewell letter.

252
00:13:27,910 --> 00:13:30,630
Chan Zhixue no longer exists.

253
00:13:30,910 --> 00:13:32,870
I hope you will return
to the right path,

254
00:13:33,030 --> 00:13:34,440
and may your future be bright.

255
00:13:35,210 --> 00:13:37,600
(Breeze Under Moonlight)
These two met through literature

256
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:39,750
and fell in love,
but could not be together.

257
00:13:41,150 --> 00:13:44,000
So, Deng Chan wrote
this farewell letter.

258
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:45,600
Tonight,

259
00:13:45,790 --> 00:13:48,390
Cheng Lei was there to meet Miss Deng.

260
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:50,120
She's been engaged
to Young Master Ziyan,

261
00:13:50,870 --> 00:13:52,640
but she has met someone
who understands her.

262
00:13:52,870 --> 00:13:54,150
This is truly a dilemma.

263
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:58,000
Mr. Deng values honor
and integrity above all,

264
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:00,840
and today their family has received

265
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,910
a chastity plaque from the Emperor.

266
00:14:04,150 --> 00:14:05,030
But Miss Deng

267
00:14:05,550 --> 00:14:07,390
has a secret relationship with a man.

268
00:14:08,390 --> 00:14:09,440
You mean...

269
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:10,960
My Lord,

270
00:14:13,900 --> 00:14:15,830
it seems something is wrong
at the Deng Mansion.

271
00:14:19,670 --> 00:14:20,550
Mr. Cheng,

272
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:23,150
my family is of a reputable lineage.

273
00:14:23,630 --> 00:14:24,820
Today we've just received

274
00:14:25,150 --> 00:14:26,670
the plaque of "A Virtuous Legacy".

275
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:27,790
Yet here you are,

276
00:14:28,150 --> 00:14:30,150
unconscious in my inner chambers.

277
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:32,600
If this word gets out,

278
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:35,030
how will I ever show my face?

279
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:38,030
My Lord, please calm down. I'm sorry.

280
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:40,600
Why did you sneak into here?

281
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:41,680
Tell me.

282
00:14:43,390 --> 00:14:45,000
I came tonight to see...

283
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:45,840
Grandfather.

284
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:49,870
Grandfather.

285
00:14:51,030 --> 00:14:52,200
Why have you come to my house?

286
00:14:55,510 --> 00:14:56,360
Chan.

287
00:14:58,360 --> 00:15:00,240
Is Mr. Cheng here to see you?

288
00:15:01,550 --> 00:15:02,390
Grandfather.

289
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,390
Let's get rid of this man first.

290
00:15:05,390 --> 00:15:06,670
Greetings, Mr. Deng.

291
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:12,910
The banquet is over.

292
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,320
What is this about?

293
00:15:14,790 --> 00:15:16,320
After the banquet was over,

294
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:19,150
we found a novel on our way out.

295
00:15:19,390 --> 00:15:20,360
So, we came to return it.

296
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:30,800
Cheng Lei.

297
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:32,840
Chan Zhixue... Chan.

298
00:15:34,630 --> 00:15:35,960
This book is filled with filth.

299
00:15:36,390 --> 00:15:37,910
Did you write all of this?

300
00:15:38,390 --> 00:15:39,230
Answer me.

301
00:15:41,670 --> 00:15:42,630
Yes.

302
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:44,040
Yes, it was me.

303
00:15:44,550 --> 00:15:45,390
Miss Deng,

304
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:47,320
don't speak nonsense
and ruin your reputation.

305
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:48,240
Chan Zhixue isn't you.

306
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:49,240
Who's speaking nonsense?

307
00:15:49,790 --> 00:15:50,910
Why did you come here today?

308
00:15:51,510 --> 00:15:53,030
Do you want to ruin

309
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:54,270
my family's reputation?

310
00:15:54,390 --> 00:15:55,230
Chan,

311
00:15:55,910 --> 00:15:57,480
you're engaged to Young Master Ziyan.

312
00:15:58,270 --> 00:15:59,200
How could you do such

313
00:15:59,390 --> 00:16:01,000
a disgraceful thing?

314
00:16:01,570 --> 00:16:02,750
Grandfather, please calm down.

315
00:16:02,790 --> 00:16:03,630
I...

316
00:16:03,750 --> 00:16:04,750
I know I was wrong.

317
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:10,200
Thank you.

318
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:12,390
This is our family matter.

319
00:16:12,390 --> 00:16:13,360
Please leave.

320
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:14,200
Mr. Deng,

321
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:15,630
if this gets out,

322
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:18,550
it will surely damage
your family's long-standing reputation.

323
00:16:19,030 --> 00:16:20,000
But don't worry.

324
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,120
My wife and I will

325
00:16:22,750 --> 00:16:24,000
keep this secret.

326
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:25,280
We won't say a word.

327
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:27,270
What do you mean?

328
00:16:27,550 --> 00:16:28,510
To keep a secret,

329
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:30,170
of course, there are conditions.

330
00:16:33,030 --> 00:16:34,550
Apart from you,

331
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,750
who else also signed

332
00:16:37,270 --> 00:16:38,750
the joint memorial?

333
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:42,240
As expected,

334
00:16:42,390 --> 00:16:43,360
you two

335
00:16:44,030 --> 00:16:45,270
are here for this.

336
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:46,750
Miss Deng Chan and I

337
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:48,240
have met before.

338
00:16:48,390 --> 00:16:49,630
I would never harm her.

339
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:51,390
About this, we will...

340
00:16:51,390 --> 00:16:52,270
Shut up.

341
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,030
As a woman,

342
00:16:54,480 --> 00:16:56,560
instead of staying home
and observing your duties,

343
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:58,480
you're constantly out in public,

344
00:16:58,870 --> 00:17:01,270
even associating
with a notorious consort.

345
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:03,910
Do you have any sense of shame left?

346
00:17:05,350 --> 00:17:06,190
Grandfather.

347
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:07,800
You...

348
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:09,150
Mr. Fu.

349
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,790
Mr. Deng, I'm afraid

350
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:12,590
her behavior

351
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:13,880
is not for you to judge.

352
00:17:14,550 --> 00:17:15,390
You...

353
00:17:17,750 --> 00:17:18,590
I've dedicated

354
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:21,110
my whole life to serving our country

355
00:17:21,110 --> 00:17:23,240
and contributed everything I can.

356
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:24,640
How can I be coerced

357
00:17:25,310 --> 00:17:26,510
by you two?

358
00:17:26,760 --> 00:17:30,010
Tomorrow, I will go to the Zhengs' place
to apologize and cancel the engagement.

359
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:32,350
Since you two have made such a mistake,

360
00:17:33,310 --> 00:17:34,550
you must marry immediately.

361
00:17:34,900 --> 00:17:35,750
It can't be delayed.

362
00:17:35,750 --> 00:17:36,590
You can't do this.

363
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:38,440
You can't do this, Father.

364
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:39,960
Father, please reconsider.

365
00:17:40,270 --> 00:17:41,270
How dare you come here?

366
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,640
Is this the daughter you raised?

367
00:17:43,830 --> 00:17:44,670
Father,

368
00:17:45,350 --> 00:17:47,350
I'm willing to be punished
at the ancestral hall,

369
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:48,760
but Chan

370
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:50,480
can't marry Mr. Cheng.

371
00:17:51,110 --> 00:17:53,310
She's been engaged since childhood.

372
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:55,550
This is known throughout the Capital.

373
00:17:55,790 --> 00:17:56,830
If we suddenly

374
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,680
let her marry someone else,

375
00:17:59,310 --> 00:18:00,160
how will she

376
00:18:00,590 --> 00:18:02,350
face others in the future, Father?

377
00:18:06,070 --> 00:18:06,920
Chan.

378
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,240
Mother,

379
00:18:10,270 --> 00:18:11,110
I'm willing.

380
00:18:12,550 --> 00:18:14,000
- Miss Deng.
- Mr. Cheng.

381
00:18:14,310 --> 00:18:15,790
What? In just a few days,

382
00:18:15,790 --> 00:18:17,310
have you fallen for another woman?

383
00:18:18,550 --> 00:18:20,280
No, I haven't.

384
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,350
Then marry me.

385
00:18:23,350 --> 00:18:24,760
- I...
- Chan.

386
00:18:25,920 --> 00:18:27,070
Don't be foolish.

387
00:18:29,350 --> 00:18:30,350
Mother, I know

388
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:32,100
you went to great lengths

389
00:18:32,110 --> 00:18:33,480
to choose Ziyan for me.

390
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:36,680
But now, I only love Mr. Cheng.

391
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:38,790
Don't persuade me anymore.

392
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:41,200
This might be better for all of us.

393
00:18:42,110 --> 00:18:43,510
Cheng Lei isn't a good match.

394
00:18:45,400 --> 00:18:48,310
You will regret it if you marry him.

395
00:18:48,640 --> 00:18:50,070
Since you say I'm not a good match,

396
00:18:50,790 --> 00:18:52,270
then what do you consider

397
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:53,590
a good match, Mrs. Deng?

398
00:18:53,590 --> 00:18:54,430
You...

399
00:18:56,350 --> 00:18:57,190
I...

400
00:18:57,590 --> 00:18:59,030
I've heard of you.

401
00:18:59,830 --> 00:19:01,640
As a student
of the Directorate of Education,

402
00:19:01,830 --> 00:19:04,030
you have little real talent.

403
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:06,160
When your parents were alive,

404
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:07,880
they were lowly merchants.

405
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,960
You donated your family wealth

406
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:11,570
to get into the Directorate of Education

407
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:12,960
and became an extra student.

408
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:16,000
You'll amount to nothing in the future.

409
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:18,680
How can my daughter

410
00:19:18,680 --> 00:19:19,880
give up Young Master Ziyan,

411
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:22,270
her childhood sweetheart
equal to her in status,

412
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:23,680
and marry you?

413
00:19:24,480 --> 00:19:25,550
Mrs. Deng, I've long heard

414
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:27,400
of your good reputation.

415
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:30,160
Everyone says you are virtuous,

416
00:19:30,170 --> 00:19:31,510
knowledgeable, and well-mannered.

417
00:19:31,830 --> 00:19:32,790
But I didn't expect you

418
00:19:33,830 --> 00:19:35,440
to be so arrogant and rude.

419
00:19:35,750 --> 00:19:37,880
- You...
- So what if my parents were merchants?

420
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:40,130
In every class,
there is a place for everyone.

421
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:41,510
My parents died early,

422
00:19:41,510 --> 00:19:43,070
leaving behind land and shops.

423
00:19:43,720 --> 00:19:45,160
Though I can't hold an official post,

424
00:19:45,160 --> 00:19:46,590
I can still support my wife and kids.

425
00:19:46,880 --> 00:19:47,790
Shut up.

426
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:51,790
When did this family

427
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:53,960
fall under your control?

428
00:19:54,750 --> 00:19:55,960
A virtuous legacy.

429
00:19:56,400 --> 00:19:57,590
A virtuous legacy.

430
00:19:58,110 --> 00:20:00,270
- The Emperor wrote this.
- Father.

431
00:20:00,270 --> 00:20:01,270
As a mother,

432
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:03,270
you've failed to teach your kids.

433
00:20:03,480 --> 00:20:05,960
How dare you kneel under the plaque

434
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:07,240
and say those shameless words?

435
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:08,920
Father...

436
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:11,200
You two

437
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:13,000
won't get your way.

438
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:16,070
My family's long-standing reputation

439
00:20:16,750 --> 00:20:18,200
wasn't built through deceit.

440
00:20:18,680 --> 00:20:20,200
It was passed down with respect

441
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:21,920
and righteousness through generations.

442
00:20:22,270 --> 00:20:23,880
Even if we're shattered to pieces

443
00:20:24,350 --> 00:20:25,830
and have to die for principles,

444
00:20:26,270 --> 00:20:27,480
the Dengs

445
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:30,160
will bear it gladly.

446
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,280
Leave!

447
00:20:33,110 --> 00:20:34,160
- Grandfather.
- Father.

448
00:20:35,030 --> 00:20:35,880
Father.

449
00:20:40,580 --> 00:20:42,740
(Calligraphy and Painting)

450
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:46,350
I didn't expect

451
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:47,960
that Mr. Deng would be willing

452
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:49,790
to let Deng Chan marry Mr. Cheng.

453
00:20:50,270 --> 00:20:51,240
Don't you think

454
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:53,110
there's something more

455
00:20:53,350 --> 00:20:54,680
between Cheng Lei and Deng Chan?

456
00:20:55,310 --> 00:20:56,720
They were both supposed to be happy

457
00:20:56,720 --> 00:20:58,410
as they were allowed
to marry each other,

458
00:20:58,480 --> 00:21:00,550
but one was in tears,

459
00:21:00,790 --> 00:21:02,640
and the other was filled
with shame and anger.

460
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,240
It's really strange.

461
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:07,880
Should I have Mu Feng and Mu Yan

462
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:09,080
keep an eye on them?

463
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:11,310
Alright.

464
00:22:06,700 --> 00:22:10,180
(Two days later)

465
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,250
What's this?

466
00:22:17,440 --> 00:22:18,590
Mu Feng just reported

467
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:21,030
that someone from the Deng family
sneaked out.

468
00:22:21,030 --> 00:22:21,870
It was Deng Chan.

469
00:22:23,200 --> 00:22:24,750
Tomorrow is the wedding day.

470
00:22:25,650 --> 00:22:27,470
Is she trying to run away
from the wedding?

471
00:22:27,480 --> 00:22:28,970
My Lord, Cheng Lei also sneaked out.

472
00:22:28,970 --> 00:22:30,580
He seems to be heading towards the east.

473
00:22:30,590 --> 00:22:32,510
Maybe he's going to see Miss Deng.

474
00:22:32,750 --> 00:22:33,590
Mu Feng said

475
00:22:34,590 --> 00:22:36,790
Miss Deng was heading towards the west.

476
00:22:38,750 --> 00:22:39,590
Let's split up.

477
00:22:39,750 --> 00:22:40,590
Alright.

478
00:22:41,590 --> 00:22:42,480
You should go.

479
00:22:43,030 --> 00:22:44,240
Leave the Capital tonight.

480
00:22:45,030 --> 00:22:46,070
I'm begging you.

481
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:47,490
I won't go.

482
00:22:47,510 --> 00:22:48,990
If I'm leaving, I'll leave with you.

483
00:22:49,030 --> 00:22:50,680
You've suffered so much in this life.

484
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:51,530
It's enough.

485
00:22:51,530 --> 00:22:52,780
You don't owe anyone anything.

486
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:54,550
Why are you being so foolish?

487
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:56,960
I've already closed my heart.

488
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:58,000
I'm shackled.

489
00:22:58,830 --> 00:23:01,110
Please stop being so childish, alright?

490
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:02,510
Ask yourself.

491
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:04,750
In your dreams of flowers and moonlight,

492
00:23:04,750 --> 00:23:06,270
have I never appeared in them?

493
00:23:07,350 --> 00:23:09,400
I love only Chan Zhixue.

494
00:23:09,940 --> 00:23:11,400
I don't care if you're young or old,

495
00:23:11,400 --> 00:23:13,110
beautiful or ugly.

496
00:23:13,350 --> 00:23:14,510
Don't you understand me?

497
00:23:14,880 --> 00:23:16,110
I was wrong.

498
00:23:17,030 --> 00:23:18,270
You can't take back

499
00:23:18,270 --> 00:23:19,810
the token of our love once it's given.

500
00:23:20,310 --> 00:23:21,750
Let me break it for you.

501
00:23:22,070 --> 00:23:23,570
Just consider that I've betrayed you.

502
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:24,480
Please forget me.

503
00:23:34,000 --> 00:23:34,840
I don't understand.

504
00:23:35,900 --> 00:23:37,440
We've known each other since childhood,

505
00:23:37,440 --> 00:23:38,840
and we're supposed to get married.

506
00:23:39,160 --> 00:23:40,000
How can that lose

507
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:41,540
to your relationship with an outsider?

508
00:23:42,110 --> 00:23:43,980
I don't believe you've fallen
for someone else.

509
00:23:46,480 --> 00:23:47,480
Don't ask me anymore.

510
00:23:49,270 --> 00:23:52,160
I've wronged your family.

511
00:23:54,270 --> 00:23:55,830
Chan, what's the real reason?

512
00:23:56,480 --> 00:23:57,320
Tell me.

513
00:23:58,160 --> 00:23:59,370
We'll figure it out together.

514
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:03,840
I...

515
00:24:03,960 --> 00:24:05,880
I never loved Cheng Lei.

516
00:24:07,270 --> 00:24:09,070
I've only loved you.

517
00:24:09,070 --> 00:24:09,910
But...

518
00:24:10,750 --> 00:24:11,680
It concerns my family.

519
00:24:12,640 --> 00:24:13,480
I...

520
00:24:13,750 --> 00:24:15,030
I have no other choice.

521
00:24:17,510 --> 00:24:18,350
Ziyan,

522
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:21,240
if you truly care for me,

523
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:24,400
stop questioning me, alright?

524
00:24:25,060 --> 00:24:26,960
Miss, we should go back now.

525
00:24:37,750 --> 00:24:38,590
It's wrong.

526
00:24:39,110 --> 00:24:40,000
Everything's wrong.

527
00:24:41,160 --> 00:24:42,240
It's my fault.

528
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:43,880
I didn't follow my duties as a woman.

529
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:45,750
I've damaged my reputation.

530
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:48,880
I shouldn't have written
such absurd things.

531
00:24:49,510 --> 00:24:50,350
It's me.

532
00:24:50,480 --> 00:24:51,400
I've ruined you.

533
00:24:52,270 --> 00:24:53,480
I've ruined Chan.

534
00:25:11,180 --> 00:25:12,020
(Legend of Huayue)

535
00:25:14,510 --> 00:25:15,350
Mother.

536
00:25:18,960 --> 00:25:19,800
Coming.

537
00:25:33,340 --> 00:25:35,500
(Hopefully, I can read the rest.)

538
00:25:39,900 --> 00:25:41,300
(Dressed in simple attire)

539
00:25:52,260 --> 00:25:53,860
(Legend of Huayue by Chan Zhixue)

540
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:00,240
(As it turns out,)

541
00:26:00,750 --> 00:26:01,880
(this is the truth.)

542
00:26:02,350 --> 00:26:03,880
It's been widely spread in the Capital

543
00:26:04,030 --> 00:26:05,510
that Mrs. Deng, Lady Zhang,

544
00:26:05,920 --> 00:26:08,030
is a woman of great chastity and virtue.

545
00:26:09,750 --> 00:26:10,880
I once thought

546
00:26:11,350 --> 00:26:12,920
you were a silent statue,

547
00:26:12,920 --> 00:26:14,690
free from sorrow or joy
and love or desire.

548
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:16,750
But that day, I realized

549
00:26:17,640 --> 00:26:20,070
you are Chan Zhixue
who wrote the Legend of Huayue.

550
00:26:21,070 --> 00:26:21,910
Do you know

551
00:26:22,640 --> 00:26:23,750
how I felt?

552
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:25,160
I don't want to know.

553
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:28,320
- I don't want to know.
- When my father was around,

554
00:26:28,790 --> 00:26:30,790
I once talked about abandoning
the scholar path.

555
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:33,760
But my father

556
00:26:36,030 --> 00:26:38,200
locked me in a dark, suffocating cellar

557
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:39,400
for three days and nights.

558
00:26:41,030 --> 00:26:42,400
After three days,

559
00:26:43,270 --> 00:26:44,550
I walked out in a daze

560
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:47,750
and looked up to see
the morning glow in the sky.

561
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:52,960
You are

562
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:56,110
that morning glow to me.

563
00:26:58,030 --> 00:26:59,550
But I'm a widow.

564
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:04,270
I'm a widow
who is 12 years older than you

565
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:08,200
