566
00:27:08,640 --> 00:27:10,270
A chastity plaque...

567
00:27:10,270 --> 00:27:11,750
Did you really care about that?

568
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:13,280
I...

569
00:27:15,310 --> 00:27:16,590
Ms. Qu in your story

570
00:27:17,160 --> 00:27:18,790
gave me the courage to abandon

571
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:20,500
the official path and enter business.

572
00:27:21,070 --> 00:27:21,910
But now,

573
00:27:22,550 --> 00:27:24,830
why don't you dare
break free from your cage?

574
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:28,240
As long as we're in love,

575
00:27:28,830 --> 00:27:30,750
what does age, status,

576
00:27:31,030 --> 00:27:32,310
or the eyes of the world matter?

577
00:27:46,310 --> 00:27:48,240
Madam, we must leave.
