578
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:50,830
Who's there?

579
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:53,840
Someone's here.

580
00:27:54,240 --> 00:27:55,110
Let's split up.

581
00:27:55,160 --> 00:27:56,000
Alright.

582
00:27:56,510 --> 00:27:57,400
Be careful.

583
00:28:08,550 --> 00:28:09,390
Father.

584
00:28:10,070 --> 00:28:10,910
Father.

585
00:28:11,510 --> 00:28:12,640
