594
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:33,240
Father,

595
00:28:35,310 --> 00:28:36,240
it's my fault.

596
00:28:37,240 --> 00:28:38,400
I failed my duties as a woman

597
00:28:38,550 --> 00:28:39,880
and went out without permission.

598
00:28:40,070 --> 00:28:41,560
It has nothing to do with anyone else.

599
00:28:42,070 --> 00:28:43,400
Father, please discern the truth.

600
00:28:43,750 --> 00:28:45,160
You're still making excuses for him.

601
00:28:45,590 --> 00:28:47,000
You can't even protect yourself.

602
00:28:47,440 --> 00:28:49,040
- Come.
- Stop.

603
00:28:53,830 --> 00:28:55,350
My Lord, it was me

604
00:28:55,750 --> 00:28:57,030
who forced Mrs. Deng to meet me.

605
00:28:57,030 --> 00:28:57,920
It's my fault.

606
00:28:58,310 --> 00:28:59,200
No, Father.

607
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:00,040
Cheng Lei...

608
00:29:01,350 --> 00:29:02,190
You...

609
00:29:02,590 --> 00:29:03,430
So,

610
00:29:03,750 --> 00:29:05,030
this obscene book

611
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:07,270
was your secret connection?

612
00:29:07,750 --> 00:29:09,270
- No, Father.
- Have you no shame?

613
00:29:09,270 --> 00:29:10,670
- Father.
- Shut up.

614
00:29:11,110 --> 00:29:13,310
You shameless, immoral woman.

615
00:29:14,550 --> 00:29:16,590
Mr. Deng, what is a woman's duty?

616
00:29:23,510 --> 00:29:25,640
Why is it that a widower can remarry

617
00:29:26,270 --> 00:29:27,680
