623
00:29:41,790 --> 00:29:42,790
We're all human.

624
00:29:42,790 --> 00:29:45,070
Are women born
to suppress their desires?

625
00:29:45,310 --> 00:29:47,440
If this is your so-called women's duty,

626
00:29:47,960 --> 00:29:50,240
then there's no need to carry it out.

627
00:29:52,400 --> 00:29:54,350
Zhuang Hanyan, it's you again.

628
00:29:54,750 --> 00:29:56,160
It must've been you

629
00:29:56,270 --> 00:29:58,590
who instigated them to commit adultery

630
00:29:58,730 --> 00:30:00,050
and ruin my family's reputation.

631
00:30:00,110 --> 00:30:01,750
You wicked woman.

632
00:30:02,160 --> 00:30:04,750
Before you got married,

633
