in public, ruining morals.

636
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:14,310
If Fu Yunxi refuses to discipline you,

637
00:30:14,310 --> 00:30:17,030
I will do it for him.

638
00:30:21,790 --> 00:30:23,280
- Mother.
- You...

639
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:24,240
Chan.

640
00:30:25,030 --> 00:30:25,870
Mr. Deng,

641
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:27,270
