642
00:30:27,270 --> 00:30:28,350
Are you going

643
00:30:29,110 --> 00:30:30,830
to slap me in the face?

644
00:30:31,070 --> 00:30:32,880
Fine.

645
00:30:33,070 --> 00:30:34,640
The public morals are falling apart.

646
00:30:35,510 --> 00:30:37,440
Rituals and laws are doomed.

647
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:39,040
Chan.

648
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:41,520
Grandfather,

649
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:43,830
for the sake of my mother's years

650
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:46,160
of loyal service to our family,

651
00:30:47,200 --> 00:30:48,040
please

652
00:30:48,590 --> 00:30:49,460
spare her.

653
00:30:49,480 --> 00:30:51,070
You're also defending her?

654
00:30:51,070 --> 00:30:52,160
Are you also going to become

655
00:30:52,160 --> 00:30:53,640
a shameless, immoral women like her?

656
00:30:53,640 --> 00:30:54,480
I...

657
00:30:55,440 --> 00:30:56,960
Chan, Chan.

658
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:58,640
Let me see it.

659
00:31:01,550 --> 00:31:03,480
If my daughter had a choice,

660
00:31:08,110 --> 00:31:09,880
I'd rather

661
00:31:13,350 --> 00:31:14,440
she never became

662
00:31:15,290 --> 00:31:16,900
a good woman like I was,

663
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:20,790
praised by everyone.

664
00:31:23,030 --> 00:31:23,960
Zhang,

665
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:25,440
how dare you speak

666
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:27,030
such reckless words?

667
00:31:30,920 --> 00:31:32,790
I just spoke the truth,

668
00:31:34,480 --> 00:31:35,750
and you can't bear it?

669
00:31:37,750 --> 00:31:38,640
Get up, Chan.

670
00:31:42,750 --> 00:31:43,590
Today,

671
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:47,070
let me tell you all the truth.

672
00:31:48,510 --> 00:31:49,880
It's been 17 years.

673
00:31:51,310 --> 00:31:53,550
I've never missed

674
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:55,200
my late husband day and night

675
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:58,200
and adhered to a woman's duty.

676
00:31:59,880 --> 00:32:02,000
I never truly loved your son.

677
00:32:02,830 --> 00:32:05,200
I've even forgotten what he looks like.

678
00:32:05,790 --> 00:32:07,590
- You...
- Between him and me,

679
00:32:08,110 --> 00:32:09,750
there was never any warmth or affection.

680
00:32:11,350 --> 00:32:12,830
He despised my poetry and literature

681
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:15,200
and burned my books.

682
00:32:15,920 --> 00:32:16,920
But I know

683
00:32:18,110 --> 00:32:19,550
he was just jealous

684
00:32:20,550 --> 00:32:21,830
and afraid.

685
00:32:23,790 --> 00:32:25,790
He was a mediocre man

686
00:32:26,440 --> 00:32:27,750
who was born

687
00:32:27,750 --> 00:32:29,920
into a scholarly family like yours.

688
00:32:30,270 --> 00:32:31,110
You...

689
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:33,840
Do you know?

690
00:32:35,750 --> 00:32:36,830
The essays of your son

691
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:39,070
that you highly praised

692
00:32:40,310 --> 00:32:41,830
were written

693
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:44,200
by me.

694
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:48,160
He stole my talent

695
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,160
while suppressing me.

696
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:52,310
Whenever he felt inferior,

697
00:32:52,880 --> 00:32:54,550
he would ignore and torment me.

698
00:32:54,550 --> 00:32:56,000
I've had enough.

699
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:58,020
I don't want to endure this any longer.

700
00:32:59,030 --> 00:33:00,510
I've had enough.

701
00:33:01,200 --> 00:33:02,550
Nonsense.

702
00:33:02,680 --> 00:33:04,700
How can you accuse my son without proof?

703
00:33:05,400 --> 00:33:07,440
You can't believe the words
of a shameless woman.

704
00:33:07,440 --> 00:33:08,510
What is a shameless woman?

705
00:33:08,530 --> 00:33:10,840
If breaking free from chains
makes me a shameless woman,

706
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:12,700
and trapping myself
makes me a virtuous woman,

707
00:33:12,720 --> 00:33:15,350
what's wrong with being
a shameless women?

708
00:33:15,350 --> 00:33:16,190
You...

709
00:33:18,830 --> 00:33:20,270
It's been 17 years.

710
00:33:20,440 --> 00:33:21,680
I've sacrificed

711
00:33:22,270 --> 00:33:23,880
17 years of my life.

712
00:33:26,750 --> 00:33:29,070
For an empty reputation,

713
00:33:29,830 --> 00:33:31,000
I've locked myself

714
00:33:32,110 --> 00:33:33,440
in a cage

715
00:33:34,920 --> 00:33:37,270
called chastity.

716
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:40,400
I've been tied to it
like it's part of my flesh,

717
00:33:41,110 --> 00:33:42,510
and it's hard for me to break free.

718
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:44,550
But today,

719
00:33:48,310 --> 00:33:49,550
I no longer wish

720
00:33:52,790 --> 00:33:53,960
to keep that chastity plaque

721
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:56,920
for you

722
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:02,400
and for your vanity.

723
00:34:03,350 --> 00:34:05,790
I want to reclaim my name.

724
00:34:12,030 --> 00:34:14,480
My name is Zhang Wanjun,

725
00:34:14,920 --> 00:34:15,880
the eldest daughter

726
00:34:16,760 --> 00:34:17,710
of the Zhang family

727
00:34:19,590 --> 00:34:20,550
in Jiying Alley.

728
00:34:23,550 --> 00:34:25,510
For my brother's career,

729
00:34:27,710 --> 00:34:29,550
for the prosperity of my family,

730
00:34:32,760 --> 00:34:33,710
and

731
00:34:34,710 --> 00:34:36,030
for my children's future,

732
00:34:37,030 --> 00:34:38,590
I've endured for many years.

733
00:34:39,280 --> 00:34:40,360
But today,

734
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:45,440
I want to live for myself.

735
00:34:48,070 --> 00:34:50,630
I want to live well.

736
00:34:51,150 --> 00:34:52,030
You've gone mad.

737
00:34:53,190 --> 00:34:54,230
You've gone mad.

738
00:34:54,230 --> 00:34:56,230
Yes, I've gone mad.

739
00:34:57,280 --> 00:34:58,550
For 17 years,

740
00:34:58,920 --> 00:35:01,710
I've shaped myself into a revered,

741
00:35:02,630 --> 00:35:04,630
untouchable figure.

742
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:05,840
Today,

743
00:35:05,840 --> 00:35:08,070
I'm going to shatter that figure
with my own hands.

744
00:35:09,070 --> 00:35:10,360
Even if it breaks,

745
00:35:12,630 --> 00:35:14,070
I can still piece it together.

746
00:35:16,960 --> 00:35:17,840
I can do it.

747
00:35:19,710 --> 00:35:20,710
I can do this.

748
00:35:26,110 --> 00:35:27,480
Even if I'm bleeding

749
00:35:28,030 --> 00:35:29,800
and covered in wounds,

750
00:35:30,400 --> 00:35:31,960
as long as my name remains,

751
00:35:35,510 --> 00:35:36,840
I am

752
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:40,510
a complete woman.

753
00:35:41,150 --> 00:35:42,840
Why can't I

754
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:45,210
have someone who understands me,

755
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:47,720
respects me,

756
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:50,550
and cherishes me to love me?

757
00:35:52,030 --> 00:35:53,110
Why can't I?

758
00:35:55,150 --> 00:35:56,280
Why can't I

759
00:35:56,400 --> 00:35:57,240
live without fear

760
00:35:58,030 --> 00:36:00,550
for once?

761
00:36:01,590 --> 00:36:02,430
Someone.

762
00:36:02,920 --> 00:36:04,280
The madam is delirious,

763
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:05,400
speaking nonsense.

764
00:36:05,760 --> 00:36:07,000
Take her back immediately,

765
00:36:07,090 --> 00:36:08,310
and confine her for treatment.

766
00:36:08,400 --> 00:36:10,280
Take the young lady back
and watch over her.

767
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:12,300
Tomorrow, she'll get married
at an auspicious time.

768
00:36:12,630 --> 00:36:15,070
Whoever obstructs my family affairs

769
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:17,230
will face my wrath.

770
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:18,680
Go.

771
00:36:19,110 --> 00:36:21,000
- Grandfather, I won't marry him.
- Go.

772
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:22,670
- No.
- I won't marry him.

773
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:23,710
I'm not afraid.

774
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:24,710
I won't marry her.

775
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:27,360
I love only Chan Zhixue.

776
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:29,320
Let me go.

777
00:36:29,550 --> 00:36:30,630
Let me go.

778
00:36:40,860 --> 00:36:44,820
(Deng Mansion)

779
00:37:21,940 --> 00:37:23,940
(Wedding procession, Zheng Mansion)

