00:37:49,190 --> 00:37:50,960
The imperial edict is in her room.

786
00:37:51,190 --> 00:37:52,630
The edict is important.

787
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:54,150
Put out the fire.

788
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:04,230
Mr. Deng,

789
00:38:05,190 --> 00:38:06,960
if you want peace in your home,

790
00:38:07,440 --> 00:38:09,110
the fire you truly need to extinguish

791
00:38:09,670 --> 00:38:10,760
is the stubborn,

792
00:38:11,030 --> 00:38:12,840
obsessive fire in your heart.

793
00:38:13,190 --> 00:38:14,030
It's you.

794
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:16,790
You let her go.

795
00:38:17,190 --> 00:38:19,840
From now on, there won't no Mrs. Deng

796
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:21,920
or the student Cheng Lei in this world.

797
00:38:22,110 --> 00:38:23,880
When did you let her go?

798
00:38:25,070 --> 00:38:26,480
Where are all my servants?

799
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:28,880
I've served
in the Judicial Review for years.

800
00:38:29,360 --> 00:38:31,070
This is just a piece of cake

801
00:38:32,710 --> 00:38:33,590
for me.

802
00:38:35,510 --> 00:38:36,590
Fu Yunxi,

803
00:38:38,150 --> 00:38:40,070
