804
00:38:40,670 --> 00:38:41,710
Don't you fear

805
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:43,880
being imprisoned or executed?

806
00:38:44,510 --> 00:38:45,670
Your chaste daughter-in-law,

807
00:38:46,230 --> 00:38:47,360
after receiving praise,

808
00:38:47,670 --> 00:38:50,190
remembered her late husband
with deep sorrow,

809
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:52,760
so today, she set herself on fire

810
00:38:53,190 --> 00:38:54,280
to join him in death.

811
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:55,680
Is Noble Consort Miao

812
00:38:56,760 --> 00:38:59,110
behind all of this?

813
00:38:59,630 --> 00:39:01,030
It's an act for the sake of justice.

814
00:39:01,280 --> 00:39:02,880
No one is behind it.

815
00:39:04,400 --> 00:39:06,360
What crime have I committed?

816
00:39:06,840 --> 00:39:09,230
Would the heavens destroy me too?

817
00:39:09,230 --> 00:39:11,230
You knew the importance
of a woman's reputation,

818
00:39:11,630 --> 00:39:13,880
yet you still insisted on tarnishing

819
00:39:14,670 --> 00:39:16,550
the name of an innocent childless woman

820
00:39:16,550 --> 00:39:18,110
in the Palace.

821
00:39:18,630 --> 00:39:19,510
Is this

822
00:39:20,510 --> 00:39:21,710
not a crime?

823
00:39:23,760 --> 00:39:25,630
Mr. Deng, you've repeatedly said

824
00:39:26,070 --> 00:39:27,800
that you must protect your family's

825
00:39:27,960 --> 00:39:29,530
long-standing reputation and foundation

826
00:39:30,480 --> 00:39:31,960
even if you're shattered to pieces

827
00:39:32,150 --> 00:39:34,630
and have to die for principles.

828
00:39:34,630 --> 00:39:36,630
Zhang Wanjun has left the Capital,

829
00:39:36,630 --> 00:39:38,480
and her name for chastity and virtue

830
00:39:39,150 --> 00:39:40,960
should be burned clean

831
00:39:41,320 --> 00:39:42,510
in this fire.

832
00:39:42,510 --> 00:39:43,350
No, no, no.

833
00:39:43,550 --> 00:39:44,390
I'll tell you.

834
00:39:44,550 --> 00:39:45,590
I'll tell you everything.

835
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:47,320
We're all ears.

836
00:39:47,440 --> 00:39:49,280
I know that everything you've done

837
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:50,760
is to help Noble Consort Miao,

838
00:39:50,760 --> 00:39:53,440
