843
00:40:01,400 --> 00:40:03,320
The one who wants
to kill Noble Consort Miao

844
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:04,960
is Yao Zhidong, Grand Secretary

845
00:40:06,040 --> 00:40:07,280
of the Hall of Literary Glory.

846
00:40:09,880 --> 00:40:10,840
What I can do

847
